body:
Exactly what the title says. As soon as I get in the Lunar Revel Shop, Kassidin pops up with Harbringer skin for 529 RP and I can not buy it. An error keeps popping up. I have tried logging on and off again and again and it still will not work. What can I do?

Error reads:

&quot;An unexpected error has occurred, please check back again later.&quot;
